    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. My students also need to address the economic side of things. They're having a hard time framing the impact of immigration on the domestic labor market and public resources in a way that sounds legitimate and not just like \"anti-immigrant\" rhetoric. Can you help them develop a sophisticated argument regarding the strain on social services and the need to protect domestic wages?",
